A crosswalk of IEP survey names

crosswalk.Rd

Relates IEP survey names to recommended names created by the DUWG

Usage

crosswalk

Format

A data frame with 29 columns

variableType

Category of variable of interest

variable

Name used to describe the data collected

recommendedName

Value recommended by IEP to use to describe the relevant data

recommendedUnit

Value recommended by IEP to use to describe the unit of the relevant data

notes

Freeform comments by IEP
